</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00127/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一个SCP基金会的Logo，任何看见它的人都会重复“收容，控制，保护”<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>[已编辑]<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>Site05的大厅<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>王特工：“收容，控制，保护。”<br />
Dr.Bert：“你已经念了这玩意45遍了&#8230;&#8230;..哦，收容，控制，保护。”</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00127" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00127" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00127-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crimaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6106971); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6106971&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247359" alt="Crimaster" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6106971)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crimaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6106971); return false;">Crimaster</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1588080081 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">28 Apr 2020 13:21</span></p>
